{"tid":2331318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港保衛戰] [英靈不滅，浩氣長存] 今日係衛港烈士奧斯本殉港日","createTime":"2020-12-18T16:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T06:39:36.000Z","uid":43150,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d05c84e6384c9ed830672fbf2bf519c26561808","tid":2331318,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Lest we forget</span></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ee/Hong_Kong_Park_statue.jpg/1280px-Hong_Kong_Park_statue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fee%2FHong_Kong_Park_statue.jpg%2F1280px-Hong_Kong_Park_statue.jpg&h=f9b672c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇喺香港公園見過依個像呀？<br />\n佢就係來自加拿大嘅軍人 <strong>John Robert Osborn, VC</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3c/John_Robert_Osborn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F3c%2FJohn_Robert_Osborn.png&h=123ed1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1941年12月18號，日軍已經登陸香港島<br />\n19號，Osborn 帶領住溫尼柏榴彈兵團A連同228聯隊打到火紅火綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日軍嘅手榴彈掟埋嚟，Osborn 執返起掟返俾佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最後都有個執唔切，電光火石之間佢以身攬住個手榴彈，保護隊友而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢事後獲追頒英帝國最高榮譽嘅軍事勳章 <strong>Victoria Cross </strong><br />\n<br />\n香港曾經有奧斯本軍營就係Name after 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大冇忘記過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watchv=mPLyGYhbedE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatchv%3DmPLyGYhbedE&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=6a306b9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watchv=mPLyGYhbedE</a>"},{"pid":"93372a3ecca6cabcf1f3b1153e316ac5a1bb1f40","tid":2331318,"uid":43150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"多謝Watershed HK嘅summary <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//赴港協防 戰至最後<br />\n<br />\n1941年11月16日抵港的溫尼伯榴彈兵營，其實被評為「不適合執行作戰任務」的C級部隊。近千人的部隊有400名新兵，當中四份之一更未曾接受基本訓練。當時英聯邦增兵東南亞，希望威嚇日本，遏止後者野心，並爭取時間重整力量。<br />\n<br />\n誰料，日軍發動南方作戰，在偷襲珍珠灣癱瘓美軍艦隊的同時，發兵掃走歐美在東南亞勢力，以圖奪取南方油田等資源，突破「ABCD包圍網」的困境，建構群島相連的防衛線。1941年12月8日，香港保衛戰揭幕，赴港協防的加拿大援軍抵港22日後，就要面對數量、裝備和訓練皆優的日軍的考驗。<br />\n<br />\n1941年12月19日，奧士本所屬的A連經渣甸山向畢拿山推進。清晨時份，為阻日軍進擊，當時兩個排近80人上刺刀，面對斜坡及從山峰來的砲火率先衝鋒。但當時帶隊的Orville McKillop中尉迷路，攻勢有分散及消散之虞。奧士本見狀，立即一馬當先重振攻勢，打到日軍後撤。<br />\n<br />\n隨後3小時，奧士本帶領部隊兩度打退兵力達三個連（約400人）的日軍反擊。約早上10時，奧士本收到命令後撤，以免部隊被孤立落單。他一邊安排部屬後退，一邊以身犯險，尋回迷路的同袍。<br />\n<br />\n其後日軍迫近，奧士本指揮士兵以兩支輕機槍還擊，掩護同袍撤退，並鼓舞落隊者堅持，維持士氣。日軍逐步包圍加軍，加軍面對四方八面而來的砲火，彈藥更見緊拙。日軍兩次攻勢被遏止後，改為向被困的加軍投擲手榴彈，奧士本成功最少將兩枚手榴彈拋回敵軍。<br />\n<br />\nA連指揮官Albert &lsquo;Granny&rsquo; Gresham少校意識到回天乏術，與奧士本商量後，就在木棒上繫上白手帕，打算投降以救活最多的同袍。可是，少校步出隨即被日軍以機槍掃射打死。其後，有一枚手榴彈落於墼壕內，位置太遠難以擲回，但爆炸的話會殺傷周遭同袍。奧士本警告Bill Pugsley上士後縱身覆蓋手榴彈，捨己救活最少6人，當場陣亡，終年42歲。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/battleofhongkong-canada-osborn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2Fbattleofhongkong-canada-osborn%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=b00699ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com/battleofhongkong-canada-osborn/</a>"},{"pid":"daeda74d4b9392d824b2af620164c933cad7b8c7","tid":2331318,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2abbe6102aac4d5c008e386ae1ba18f7e7d7f3","tid":2331318,"uid":43150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"大家請like Watershed HK Facebook, Instagram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPatreon更加好唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申唔識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9727dce4bc5622dacad7272ff1b5f955bad2c969","tid":2331318,"uid":103239,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補番個佢哋啱啱出，關於奧士本嘅勳章故事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CI5PZZXgqhn/?igshid=1xe328ykrajzl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCI5PZZXgqhn%2F%3Figshid%3D1xe328ykrajzl&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBUqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=8d1c19ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCI5PZZXgqhn%2F%3Figshid%3D1xe328ykrajzl&h=6165da06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CI5PZZXgqhn/?igshid=1xe328ykrajzl</a>"},{"pid":"8e8645e5529925fd64ac13fefbf7a13a54f58ba1","tid":2331318,"uid":306699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1093623bc37c6c6354253529dfc3374f1be5254","tid":2331318,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"captain hongkong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaf9a5aef655d3bc74719b122c74386a78a5ee6","tid":2331318,"uid":232306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有香港公園個銅像"},{"pid":"b3e9853e313dbc0b81732d86b03464d798552a6b","tid":2331318,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c28d0b4c48adbb9fcc55ea186d0c6b7a531b53a8","tid":2331318,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"932cc20f8cbb3ff9729520f04e4b0c11bd995dce","tid":2331318,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c8f776fc9bba52440b0f96290db99f519fbaa2","tid":2331318,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b6/Brigadier_John_K._Lawson_%28c.1941%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb6%2FBrigadier_John_K._Lawson_%2528c.1941%2529.jpg&h=2cb4aabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有加拿大援軍兼西旅指揮官羅遜准將，係突圍時陣亡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5020911ce8d5e02aeecb285fe4346d973e9faf51","tid":2331318,"uid":364831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d05c84e6384c9ed830672fbf2bf519c26561808","tid":2331318,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">Lest we forget</span></strong> <